reviewText: Ummm... i ordered this and cannot use it.  The disks are formatted differently and cannot be played on my dvd player.  Also the writing for the episode table of contents is in German.
couldnt of gone better. well worth the money and wait to get it. any fan of power rangers should get this
I bought this as a christmas gift for my son and it is in german and cannot be played because it is out of region

received well before estimated delivery date and product was exactly as described.  one of the better seasons of the power rangers.  but if you are a fan of the power rangers you won't be disappointed.
this is a sweet thing to have for your collection. the cover is awesome. the cds work wonders, loving it
